AI-Powered Smart Healthcare Management System
End-to-End Digital Healthcare Platform (ML + DL + AI + Realtime Chat + E-Pharmacy + Analytics)
 Overview

This project is a full-stack intelligent healthcare ecosystem built using Flask + MongoDB + AI + ML + DL + Realtime Communication.
It integrates patient care, doctor workflows, medicine ordering, health analytics, image-based diagnosis, and AI assistance — all in one platform.

This is a production-grade capstone project with rich features such as:

1.Patient & Doctor Login / Signup
2.Realtime Chat (Socket.IO)
3.Appointment Booking System
4.Diagnostics Test Center Booking
5.ML Disease Prediction Models
6.DL Skin Disease Detection
7.Prescription OCR
8.E-Pharmacy (Cart + Orders + Stock)
9.AI-powered Suggestions (Gemini API)
10.Health Statistics With Charts
11.Admin Dashboard
12.Email Alerts using SendGrid

This project is suitable for:
Academic / Capstone Projects
Real-world healthcare prototypes
Industry-level demos
Research extensions
Startup MVP

Tech Stack
1.Frontend
HTML5, CSS3
JavaScript
Chart.js
Socket.IO Client
2.Backend
Python Flask
Flask-SocketIO
Apscheduler
EasyOCR
TensorFlow / Keras
Scikit-Learn
XGBoost
Gradient Boosting
Gemini AI
3.Database
MongoDB Atlas (Cloud NoSQL)
Email
SendGrid API

AI, ML & DL Components
1. Machine Learning Models
Disease	Model	Features Used
Heart Disease Prediction	Naive Bayes	BP, Cholesterol, Age, etc.
Diabetes Prediction	XGBoost	Glucose, BMI, Age, etc.
Stroke Prediction	Gradient Boosting	BP, BMI, Work Type, etc.

Models are trained and stored as .pkl files.

2. Deep Learning

Skin Disease Classification using MobileNetV2
Classifies skin images
Outputs disease name + confidence

Fast and accurate
OCR + AI
Prescription Checker using EasyOCR
Extracts handwritten/printed text from images
Text is analyzed by Gemini AI
Produces patient-friendly explanation
AI Health Advisor
Using Gemini 2.5 API:
Based on uploaded stats and trends
Gives personalized health suggestions

User Roles
Role	Capabilities
Patient	Book appointments, chat with doctors, order medicines, upload stats, view analytics, OCR prescriptions
Doctor	Realtime chat, view patient queries, respond, get notified
Admin	Manage doctors, approve registrations, overall monitoring

Major Features
1. Realtime Chat (Doctor ↔ Patient)
Built using Socket.IO

Typing indicators
Chat history stored
Email alerts on new messages
Works even with low internet (fallback polling)

2. Appointment Booking System
Select doctor
Select date & time slot
Detects slot conflicts
Suggests alternate options
Sends email reminders
Saves to bookings collection

3. Diagnostics Marketplace
Patients can book:
Blood tests
X-ray
CT scan
MRI
Master health checkup
Each test center has:
Hourly slots
Unique tokens
Booking history
Stored in test_centers collection.

4. E-Pharmacy System
Browse medicines
Add to cart
Remove items
Place order
Auto stock reduction
Orders stored in orders collection
Cart stored in carts collection
Each medicine has:
Price
Uses
Stock count
Email confirmation sent on purchase.

5. Health Statistics Dashboard
Patients can upload:
Blood Pressure
Sugar Level
Heart Rate
Weight

Shown through:
Bar Chart
Line Chart (Trend)
AI Health Advice

Records stored in health_stats.

6. Prescription Checker (OCR + AI Explanation)

Flow:
Upload prescription image
EasyOCR extracts text
Gemini AI explains:
Medicines
Dosage
Purposes
Precautions
Saved in database

7. Disease Prediction Modules
Machine Learning models predict:

Heart disease risk
Diabetes risk
Stroke risk

Each prediction includes:
Probability
Risk classification
AI-based explanation

8. Deep Learning: Skin Disease Detection
MobileNetV2
High accuracy
Upload skin lesion image
Returns:
Prediction
Confidence
Care instructions

9. Admin Panel

View all doctors
Approve doctors
Admin login
System-level controls

